==产品==
===当前===
截至2014年8月，默克获批的药品数量是所有制药公司中最多的，由默克研发并被FDA批准的新分子实体数量为63个。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=An overview of FDA-approved new molecular entities: 1827–2013|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1359644614001032|last=Kinch|first=Michael S.|last2=Haynesworth|first2=Austin|date=2014-08-01|journal=Drug Discovery Today|issue=8|doi=10.1016/j.drudis.2014.03.018|volume=19|pages=1033–1039|language=en|issn=1359-6446|last3=Kinch|first3=Sarah L.|last4=Hoyer|first4=Denton|access-date=2020-06-15|archive-date=2020-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615205211/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1359644614001032|dead-url=no}}</ref>默沙东在中国提供涵盖心血管、抗感染、男性健康、女性健康、骨科、疼痛、皮肤、呼吸、糖尿病、专科药品、辅助生殖等领域的42种人用药品和疫苗，并向中国市场提供46种动物保健产品，用以预防和治疗家禽家畜以及宠物的疾病。<ref name="MSD_China_Products">{{cite web| url=http://www.msdchina.com.cn/product/pages/home.aspx| title=公司产品| accessdate=9 October 2015| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024025144/http://www.msdchina.com.cn/product/pages/home.aspx| archivedate=2015年10月24日| df=}}</ref>

在2014年，默克的产品包括：<ref>{{Cite web|title=MRK 12.31.2013 10K|url=https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/310158/000031015814000009/mrk1231201310k.htm|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=www.sec.gov|archive-date=2020-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822190909/https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/310158/000031015814000009/mrk1231201310k.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

*[[西格列汀|捷诺维]]（Januvia，[[西格列汀|西格列汀]]），用于治疗2型糖尿病的二肽基肽酶-4抑制剂。2013年，捷诺维是世界上销量第二高的抗糖尿病药，<ref>{{Cite web|title=The top 10 best-selling diabetes drugs of 2013|url=https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/top-10-best-selling-diabetes-drugs-of-2013|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=FiercePharma|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227044300/https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/top-10-best-selling-diabetes-drugs-of-2013|dead-url=no}}</ref>销售额约40亿美元。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Sitagliptin in the treatment of type 2 diabetes: a meta-analysis|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1756-5391.2012.01189.x|last=Zhan|first=Mei|last2=Xu|first2=Ting|date=2012|journal=Journal of Evidence-Based Medicine|issue=3|doi=10.1111/j.1756-5391.2012.01189.x|volume=5|pages=154–165|language=en|issn=1756-5391|last3=Wu|first3=Fengbo|last4=Tang|first4=Yao|access-date=2020-06-15|archive-date=2020-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615205208/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1756-5391.2012.01189.x|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Glycaemic efficacy of glucagon-like peptide-1 receptor agonists and dipeptidyl peptidase-4 inhibitors as add-on therapy to metformin in subjects with type 2 diabetes—a review and meta analysis|url=https://dom-pubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1463-1326.2012.01603.x|last=Deacon|first=C. F.|last2=Mannucci|first2=E.|date=2012-08-01|journal=Diabetes, Obesity and Metabolism|issue=8|doi=10.1111/j.1463-1326.2012.01603.x|volume=14|pages=762–767|issn=1462-8902|last3=Ahrén|first3=B.|access-date=2020-06-15|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501115930/https://dom-pubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1463-1326.2012.01603.x|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Incretin treatment and risk of pancreatitis in patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus: systematic review and meta-analysis of randomised and non-randomised studies|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3987051/|last=Li|first=Ling|last2=Shen|first2=Jiantong|date=2014-04-15|journal=The BMJ|doi=10.1136/bmj.g2366|volume=348|issn=0959-8138|pmc=3987051|pmid=24736555|last3=Bala|first3=Malgorzata M|last4=Busse|first4=Jason W|last5=Ebrahim|first5=Shanil|last6=Vandvik|first6=Per Olav|last7=Rios|first7=Lorena P|last8=Malaga|first8=German|last9=Wong|first9=Evelyn|access-date=2020-06-15|archive-date=2014-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520235443/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3987051/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

* [[艾洛松|艾洛松]]（Eloson，[[糠酸莫米松|糠酸莫米松]]）是一种常用的[[糖皮质激素|糖皮质激素]]类皮肤用药，常用于治疗皮炎。<ref name="MSD_China_Products"/>

* [[瑞美隆|瑞美隆]]（Remeron，[[米氮平|米氮平]]）是一种[[NaSSA|NaSSA]]类[[抗抑郁药|抗抑郁药]]，用于治疗抑郁症。<ref name="MSD_China_Products"/>

*[[氯雷他定|开瑞坦]]（Claritin，[[氯雷他定|氯雷他定]]）是一种抗过敏药，用于缓解过敏性鼻炎有关的症状。<ref name="MSD_China_Products"/>

*[[辛伐他汀|舒降之]]（Zocor，[[辛伐他汀|辛伐他汀]]）是一种他汀类药物，用于治疗高脂血症。<ref name="MSD_China_Products"/>

* [[Zetia|Zetia]]（[[依泽替米贝|依泽替米贝]]，ezetimibe）是一种通过抑制胆固醇吸收来治疗高胆固醇血症的药物，但是争议较大。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.medpagetoday.com/MeetingCoverage/AHA/48637 | work=MedpageToday | title=AHA: IMPROVE-IT Proves Ezetimibe Benefit | date=November 17, 2014 | accessdate=2016-06-11 | archive-date=2018-10-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005000519/https://www.medpagetoday.com/meetingcoverage/aha/48637 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

* [[Remicade|Remicade]] ([[英利昔单抗|英利昔单抗]]，infliximab）是一种单克隆抗体，目标为细胞因子[[肿瘤坏死因子-α|TNF-α]]，用于治疗自体免疫疾病。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis of the Efficacy and Safety of Existing TNF Blocking Agents in Treatment of Rheumatoid Arthritis|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3260264/|last=Aaltonen|first=Kalle J.|last2=Virkki|first2=Liisa M.|date=2012-01-17|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=1|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0030275|volume=7|issn=1932-6203|pmc=3260264|pmid=22272322|last3=Malmivaara|first3=Antti|last4=Konttinen|first4=Yrjö T.|last5=Nordström|first5=Dan C.|last6=Blom|first6=Marja|access-date=2020-06-15|archive-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609115745/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3260264/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

* [[加德西|加德西]]（Gardasil，重组人类乳头状瘤病毒疫苗）是针对多种血清型[[人類乳突病毒|人类乳头瘤病毒]]（HPV）的疫苗。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.merck.com/product/usa/pi_circulars/g/gardasil/gardasil_pi.pdf |title=www.merck.com |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2012-03-18 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66GSUD1h0?url=http://www.merck.com/product/usa/pi_circulars/g/gardasil/gardasil_pi.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

* [[艾生特|艾生特]]（Isentress，[[拉替拉韦|拉替拉韦]]）是人类免疫缺陷病毒整合酶抑制剂，用于治疗艾滋病毒感染。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.merck.com/product/usa/pi_circulars/i/isentress/isentress_pi.pdf |title=www.merck.com |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2021-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523042028/https://www.merck.com/product/usa/pi_circulars/i/isentress/isentress_pi.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2013年销售额为18亿美元。拉替拉韦是美国卫生及公共服务部推荐的多种艾滋病一线药物之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/contentfiles/lvguidelines/adultandadolescentgl.pdf |title=aidsinfo.nih.gov |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2016-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101202407/https://aidsinfo.nih.gov/contentfiles/lvguidelines/adultandadolescentgl.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

* [[Keytruda|Keytruda]] （pembrolizumab）是一种用于治疗癌症的免疫调节剂。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.genengnews.com/gen-news-highlights/merck-melanoma-drug-is-first-pd-1-inhibitor-ok-d-by-fda/81250309/|title=Merck Melanoma Drug Is First PD-1 Inhibitor OK'd by FDA|work=GEN|accessdate=3 July 2015|archive-date=2017-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711050006/http://www.genengnews.com/gen-news-highlights/merck-melanoma-drug-is-first-pd-1-inhibitor-ok-d-by-fda/81250309|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.accessdata.fda.gov/drugsatfda_docs/label/2014/125514lbl.pdf |title=www.accessdata.fda.gov |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325005523/https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/drugsatfda_docs/label/2014/125514lbl.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*[[厄他培南|怡万之]] (Invanz，[[厄他培南|厄他培南]]) 是一种注射用抗生素。<ref name=":0" />

===疫苗===
默克公司开发的具有重要医学价值的疫苗包括第一种[[腮腺炎疫苗|腮腺炎疫苗]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mumps|url=https://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/articles/mumps|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=History of Vaccines|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210504201757/https://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/articles/mumps|dead-url=no}}</ref>、第一种[[风疹疫苗|风疹疫苗]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rubella|url=https://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/articles/rubella|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=History of Vaccines|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501040150/https://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/articles/rubella|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[麻腮风三联疫苗|麻疹腮腺炎风疹三联减毒活疫苗]]（MMR，默尔康®）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Timeline|url=https://www.historyofvaccines.org/timeline/measles|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=History of Vaccines|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410063348/http://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/timelines/measles|archive-date=2016-04-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，疫苗均由默克公司的科学家[[莫里斯·希勒曼|莫里斯·希勒曼]]所领导的团队开发<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Maurice Hilleman: Creator of Vaccines That Changed the World|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7150172/|last=Tulchinsky|first=Theodore H.|date=2018|journal=Case Studies in Public Health|doi=10.1016/B978-0-12-804571-8.00003-2|pages=443–470|pmc=7150172|access-date=2021-08-15|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117040546/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7150172/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在美国，疫苗上市后，风疹相关的出生缺陷几率从原来的每年一万例下降到每年无新发病例<ref>{{cite web |url=http://embryology.med.unsw.edu.au/embryology/index.php?title=Abnormal_Development_-_Rubella_Virus |title=Rubella |accessdate=2014-09-22 |archive-date=2021-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512152244/https://embryology.med.unsw.edu.au/embryology/index.php?title=Abnormal_Development_-_Rubella_Virus |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

希勒曼的团队也开发出了第一种[[乙肝疫苗|乙肝疫苗]]，以及[[水痘疫苗|水痘疫苗]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/timelines/others#EVT_100763 | title=1981-Hepatitis B: First Subunit Viral Vaccine in U.S. | accessdate=2016-06-11 | archive-date=2015-02-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211100824/http://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/timelines/others#EVT_100763 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/timelines/others#EVT_100763 | title=3/17/1995-Chickenpox Vaccine Licensed | accessdate=2016-06-11 | archive-date=2015-02-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211100824/http://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/timelines/others#EVT_100763 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。1989年，默克公司将重组酵母乙肝疫苗技术技术转让中国，并于1993年在北京和深圳组建了生产工廠<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=乙肝疫苗技术转让中国30周年， 默沙东参与者追忆历史细节|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_4919178|access-date=|date=2019-11-10|last=|work=|publisher=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709040408/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_4919178|archive-date=2021-07-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":22">{{Cite web|title=一支疫苗里的合作“基因”|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2019-12/04/c_1125304625.htm|access-date=|date=2019-12-04|work=[[新华网|新华网]]|publisher=《[[中国青年报|中国青年报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202104158/http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2019-12/04/c_1125304625.htm|archive-date=2021-02-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===噻嗪类抗高血压药===
默克公司的Karl H. Beyer, James M. Sprague, John E. Baer 和Frederick C. Novello在20世纪50年代研发出了[[噻嗪类|噻嗪类]][[利尿剂|利尿剂]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Chlorothiazide. How the thiazides evolved as antihypertensive therapy.|url=https://www.ahajournals.org/doi/10.1161/01.HYP.22.3.388|last=Beyer K H|date=1993-09-01|journal=Hypertension|issue=3|doi=10.1161/01.HYP.22.3.388|volume=22|pages=388–391|access-date=2020-06-15|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729111945/https://www.ahajournals.org/doi/10.1161/01.HYP.22.3.388|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并且在1958年上市了第一种此类药物[[氯噻嗪|氯噻嗪]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Drugs@FDA: FDA-Approved Drugs|url=https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/scripts/cder/daf/|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=www.accessdata.fda.gov|archive-date=2014-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811041356/http://www.accessdata.fda.gov/scripts/cder/drugsatfda/index.cfm?fuseaction=Search.Overview&DrugName=SIMVASTATIN|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[拉斯克基金會|拉斯克基金会]]在1975年向默克公司颁发了特殊的公共健康奖，原因为“氯噻嗪挽救了数千人的生命，并且让数以百万计的高血压患者的痛苦得以缓解”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Historical Awards|url=http://www.laskerfoundation.org/awards/show/historical-awards/|accessdate=2020-06-15|last=Foundation|first=Lasker|work=The Lasker Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223033435/http://www.laskerfoundation.org/awards/formaward.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===第一种他汀类药物===
默克公司的科学家开发出了第一种[[羟甲基戊二酸单酰辅酶A还原酶抑制剂|他汀类]]药物[[洛伐他汀|洛伐他汀]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Merck: 125 years of making history|url=http://www.merck.com/about/our-history/home.html|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=merck.com|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806224716/https://www.merck.com/about/our-history/home.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，后来又开发出了同类药物[[辛伐他汀|辛伐他汀]]。

===新冠口服药===
当地时间2021年10月1日，默克公司发表声明，称中期试验表明其新冠口服药Molnupiravir可將确诊病例的住院風險降低大约50%。[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]报道称该口服药5天的疗程价格大约700美元<ref>{{Cite web|title=默沙東COVID-19口服藥是疫情扭轉者？效果、副作用一次看懂|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202110070188.aspx|accessdate=2021-11-06|work=中央社|date=2021-10-07|archive-date=2021-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108055143/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202110070188.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

当地时间2021年11月4日，英国政府发表公告，批准使用默克公司的新冠口服药Molnupiravir，并且已于2021年10月20日宣布向默克公司采购40万份疗程。该药物一天服用两次，每次4粒，持续5天<ref>{{Cite web|title=First oral antiviral for COVID-19, Lagevrio (molnupiravir), approved by MHRA|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/first-oral-antiviral-for-covid-19-lagevrio-molnupiravir-approved-by-mhra|accessdate=2021-11-06|work=UK.GOV|date=2021-11-04|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105183439/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/first-oral-antiviral-for-covid-19-lagevrio-molnupiravir-approved-by-mhra|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=英國率先通過默沙東口服藥 僅准有重症危險因子者使用|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202111040345.aspx|accessdate=2021-11-06|work=中央社|date=2021-11-04|archive-date=2021-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211130140447/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202111040345.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==社会与文化==
===患者援助项目===
默克公司是美国第一个为无法承担医药费的患者提供援助的制药公司，该项目始于20世纪50年代。<ref>[http://www.merck.com/newsroom/press_releases/corporate/2006_0526.html "Merck to Create New Patient Assistance Program for Vaccines"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.merck.com/newsroom/press_releases/corporate/2006_0526.html |date=20080916195646 }} Retrieved May 20, 2008.</ref>默克公司提供7个患者援助项目，每个项目都有着不同的具体资格要求。<ref>[http://patientassistance.com/programs.html?pharmaname=merck+%26+co&medication=&submit=Search "Patient Assistance – Available Prescription Assistance Programs From Merck & Co."] {{Wayback|url=http://patientassistance.com/programs.html?pharmaname=merck+%26+co&medication=&submit=Search |date=20120320112434 }} Retrieved May 20, 2008.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.merck.com/responsibility/pap-information.html |title=Merck Patient Assistance Programs |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2011-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727152434/http://www.merck.com/responsibility/pap-information.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===希勒曼实验室===
默克和[[威康信托基金会|威康信托基金会]]共同出资成立了位于[[印度|印度]]的非盈利研究机构{{le|希勒曼实验室|Hilleman Laboratories}}，以纪念默克药厂的知名疫苗学家[[莫里斯·希勒曼|莫里斯·希勒曼]]，该实验室致力于为[[发展中国家|发展中国家]]开发廉价[[疫苗|疫苗]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hilleman Labs|url=http://www.hilleman-labs.org/|access-date=2021-08-15|work=www.hilleman-labs.org|archive-date=2022-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220302223214/https://hilleman-labs.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当前这个项目包括开发用于预防[[霍乱|霍乱]]、[[轮状病毒|轮状病毒]]和[[脑膜炎|脑膜炎]]的成本低、热稳定的疫苗。

